Ask HN: Is there a ChatGPT “in a box” for private data?
text:
For example, say I want to upload a few gigabytes of proprietary text from business and have it be a knowledge database or private knowledge.

An example of this is: https://huberman.rile.yt/ which is for Huberman lab podcast.

The developer describes it here: https://twitter.com/rileytomasek/status/1603854647575384067

As a non-programmer I'm not sure how this was done, but wondering if there is a open source or no-code / turn key solution available.
